-Father also listed. Both surrendered on June 5th 1865. Both men were Privates in Company G of McCray's 45th Mounted Brigade. Enlisted in Powhatan AR. Information claims to be from a book called Forty-Fifth Arkansas Confederate Cavalry by Desmond Walls Allen. The book was published in 1988 and I cannot find it for sale anywhere and the nearest library that has it is over 150 miles away.
